\pard\qc\b\f0\fs32\sa240 Appendix: Full Source Code Listing\par
\pard\qc\f0\fs24\sa160 Secure Cloud-Based Electronic Health Record System with Role-Based Access Control\par
\pard\qc\f0\fs22\sa120 Prepared as a dissertation appendix document for Microsoft Word.\par
\pard\qc\f0\fs20\sa120 Generated on 19 April 2026\par
\pard\sa120\par
\pard\b\f0\fs22\sa180 Included source code scope:\par
\pard\f0\fs20\sa100 Backend: server setup, database configuration, seed script, middleware, routes, and package configuration.\par
\pard\f0\fs20\sa100 Frontend: login page, access page, stylesheet, shared JavaScript, and role-specific dashboards.\par
\pard\f0\fs20\sa100 Excluded items: node_modules, SQLite database binaries, and package-lock.json because they are generated or third-party dependency artifacts.\par
\pard\sa120\par
\pard\b\f0\fs22\sa180 How the implemented system works:\par
\pard\f0\fs19\li360\sa70 - A user opens the login page, enters credentials, and the frontend submits the request to the authentication API.\par
\pard\f0\fs19\li360\sa70 - The backend verifies the credentials, creates a JWT session token, and returns the user role together with identity details.\par
\pard\f0\fs19\li360\sa70 - The frontend stores the token locally and redirects the user to the correct dashboard for admin, clinician, or patient access.\par
\pard\f0\fs19\li360\sa70 - Each dashboard calls only the API routes relevant to that role, while the backend middleware validates tokens and checks roles before responding.\par
\pard\f0\fs19\li360\sa70 - All major access decisions are written to the audit log, and all operational data is stored in the SQLite database.\par
\pard\sa120\par
\pard\b\f0\fs22\sa180 How this appendix is organised:\par
\pard\f0\fs19\li360\sa70 - Each appendix section begins with a short description of the file\u\u\us purpose in the system.\par
\pard\f0\fs19\li360\sa70 - A second note explains how that file is used during system execution or user interaction.\par
\pard\f0\fs19\li360\sa70 - A short responsibility list summarises the main features implemented in that file.\par
\pard\f0\fs19\li360\sa70 - The complete file contents are then reproduced in full with line numbers for dissertation reference.\par
\page
